Most Recent
Mario Valerio D wrote a review Dec 2019
Perth, Australia1 contribution2 helpful votes
Friendly personnel, excellent service
I and my wife have spent 5 nights in the hotel, which is situated in a secondary, quiet street, close to the beach. The hotel self has no sight outwards, but the rooms have their outlooks towards an inner yard, where there is a nice, small and aesthetically pleasant arranged swimming pool. The rooms are spacious enough and clean. The washing sink is separated from the actual bathroom, so that two persons can use the services at same time. The personnel is outstanding friendly and helpful; they all speak good English and provide all the attentions one can wish. The hotel provides also motorbikes to rent, so that we could ride around Da Nang and spend a nice vacation there. We have to thank them for their courtesy and the good mood they can spread around.
Read more
Date of stay: December 2019
